sentences: Lars "Lasse" Nils Berghagen (born 13 May 1945) is a Swedish singer, songwriter and actor.
He released his first record in 1965, aged just 19.
Four years later, in 1969, he released the single Teddybjörnen Fredriksson ("The Teddybear Fredriksson"), which has become a classic.
